descr: "A concept that may be defined by a formal reference to a terminology or ontology or may be provided by text."

fields.name: text
fields.descr: "A human language representation of the concept as seen/selected/uttered by the user who entered the data and/or which represents the intended meaning of the user."

fields.name: id
fields.descr:
